---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Blog"
titleSuffix: " — SyncReach"
description: "SEO-focused insights on law-firm growth: client intake, marketing, automation, and building a system that turns attention into clients."
permalink: /blog/
---
<header class="phead">
  <span class="phead__motif" data-globe></span>
  <div class="phead__in">
    <span class="eyebrow">SyncReach Blog</span>
    <h1>Insights for growing law firms.</h1>
    <p>Practical thinking on client intake, marketing, automation, and building a growth system your firm actually controls.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="sec">
  {% set posts = collections.posts | reverse %}
  {% if posts | length %}
  <div class="postgrid">
    {% for post in posts %}
    <a class="pcard" href="{{ post.url }}">
      {% if post.data.cover %}<img class="pcard__img" src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">{% endif %}
      <div class="pcard__body">
        <span class="pcard__meta">{{ post.data.date | readableDate }}{% if post.data.author %} · {{ post.data.author }}{% endif %}</span>
        <h2 class="pcard__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="pcard__excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt or post.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="pcard__more">Read article <span data-arrow style="width:15px;height:15px;display:inline-flex;"></span></span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="empty">No articles published yet — check back soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
